{
  "stem": "1413.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was sitting in a taxi, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was sitting with the driver and they were sitting behind me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] They asked me-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they didn't face me, because they were sitting in back of me-- they called the names.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did this one come back?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'd say, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every one of the children, they asked me-- I had to say no.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was something for a man, 22 years old I was at the time, to tell my in-laws that their children didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] I went through something in my life, for what Hitler started.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I didn't live long life, I lived more than one life in all different ways.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My second wife, like my first wife, I met her at a dance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 19-- September of 1945.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She lost her husband.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I lost my wife.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were-- we know each other's-- each other's pain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she had only a sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had no blood relative, only my nephew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I found out later who was with a farmers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I've got a picture of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took him in as a boy-- as a baby.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was born in '41-- November '41.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took him, I think, in '43, because he was a year and a half, the farmers took him in, gave him a different name.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When I saw-- when I saw him, they didn't even have to tell me it was him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He looked like his father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] There were three kids living there-- I knew it was him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I found out one day he was alive, with the farmers who took him in.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
